							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hey all, I suggest that we get together and write down the effects of the various potions and poisons around norrath, and hopefully try to get this site going with this information. Right now the biggest turn off for Alchemist is the lack of information you get when crafting your potions and poisons, that you dont know what they do until you craft it and test it out. Hopefully once we do this people will see how strong potions and poisons really are. This way hopefully we can get some business for making them. <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Lets start getting this information together!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
