						<tr>
							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well I posted this information on the thread above, but I guess I can put it here as well:
<br />

<br />
Feriocious Corruption
<br />
Lev. 4 - Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Chloro Resin
<br />

<br />
Unimaginable Agony
<br />
Lev. 4 - Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Chloro Oil
<br />

<br />
Vengance of the Fallen
<br />
Lev. 4 - Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Chloro Wash
<br />

<br />
Influence of Hate
<br />
Lev. 5 - Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Snakeroot Oil
<br />

<br />
Mystical Influence
<br />
Lev. 5- Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Snakeroot Resin
<br />

<br />
Ravenous Incapacitation
<br />
Lev. 5- Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Snakeroot Wash
<br />

<br />
Abnormal Decline
<br />
Lev. 6- Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Milkweed Oil
<br />

<br />
Spinechill
<br />
Lev. 6 - Chem Table -  worked poison vial/ suspension/ Milkweed Wash
<br />

<br />
Untimely Concussion
<br />
Lev. 6 - Chem Table - worked poison vial/ suspension/ Milkweed Resin
<br />

<br />
Ingredients - 
<br />
Chloro Resin - Raw Elm or Roots/ liquid - Lev. 3
<br />
Chloro Oil - Raw organic plant / liquid - Lev. 3
<br />
Chloro Wash - Raw average plant/ liquid - Lev. 3
<br />
Snakeroot Oil - Snakeroot/ liquid - Lev. 3
<br />
Snakeroot Resin - Snakeroot/ liquid - Lev. 3
<br />
Snakeroot Wash - Snakeroot/ liquid - Lev. 3
<br />
Milkweed Oil - Milkweed/ liquid - Lev. 3
<br />
Milkweed Wash - Milkweed/ aerated mineral water - Lev. 3
<br />
Milkweed Resin -  Milkweed/ aerated mineral water - Lev. 3
<br />

<br />
Vials - 
<br />
Worked Poison Vial
<br />
Lev. 3 - Work bench - Isonoid Loam/ Chloro Oil/ Chloro Resin</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
						</tr>
					</table></td>
				</tr>
