<br />

<br />
It ends up costing about 1s to make, but dispells all divine, mental, and magical status effects on you, including those annoying DoTs priest mobs cast on you. It helps a bit but can also fail at breaking high level things... However when you make a stack of them for close to 20s and taking over 30 minutes to an hour to make them all, it does kinda get on your nerves how fast you can go through them.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="Razz" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
